      "Title": "OSL.SecureSave.Runtime.OSLSaveManager",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/OSL.SecureSave.Runtime.OSLSaveManager.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Client-side facade for the OSL Secure Save system.\nAll write operations are routed through the 'osl_master_save'\nCloud Code endpoint, which performs authoritative validation.</p>\n<p sourcefile=\"api/OSL.SecureSave.Runtime.OSLSaveManager.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"5\">NOTE:</p>\n<ul sourcefile=\"api/OSL.SecureSave.Runtime.OSLSaveManager.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"6\">\n<li sourcefile=\"api/OSL.SecureSave.Runtime.OSLSaveManager.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"6\">This wrapper assumes UnityServices.InitializeAsync() and\nAuthenticationService sign-in have already been performed by the\nhost application before any OSLSaveManager call is made.</li>\n<li sourcefile=\"api/OSL.SecureSave.Runtime.OSLSaveManager.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"9\">The compile guard OSL_UGS_CLOUDCODE is expected to be defined\nonce the UGS Cloud Code package (com.unity.services.cloudcode)\nis present in the project.</li>\n</ul>\n"
    },
