      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/OSL.SecureSave.Runtime.OperationType.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Operation type the client is allowed to perform on a given key.\nAddOnly : only incremental delta is permitted (e.g. currency earned).\nReplace : only absolute overwrite is permitted (e.g. current level).\nBoth    : both AddOnly and Replace are permitted.</p>\n"
