      "Title": "OSL.SocialLogin.SocialLoginManager",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/OSL.SocialLogin.SocialLoginManager.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Central entry point that routes login requests to the correct provider\nimplementation. Register concrete providers at startup (typically inside\na bootstrap MonoBehaviour) and call <xref href=\"OSL.SocialLogin.SocialLoginManager.LoginAsync(OSL.SocialLogin.ProviderKind)\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> with the\n<xref href=\"OSL.SocialLogin.ProviderKind\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> you want to use.</p>\n"
